### 파일 4: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/dto/follow/FollowUserProjection.kt`

```kotlin
// FollowUserProjection.kt - AFTER (필요한 필드만 담는 Projection DTO)
data class FollowUserProjection(
    val userId: String,
    val nickname: String,
    val profileImageUrl: String?,
